snippet.title: Fishhead 3 [walkthrough]  Intro + The Green Hills
snippet.description:
Fishhead 3 is a great freeware game from 2003. Classic old-style platform game with challenging difficulty and nice level design.

You can download Fishhead 3 here:
http://www.freegamearchive.com/download-game/game/11296

Part 2 (The Snowfields)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bDhIPlASCqE
Part 3 (The Ancient Swamp)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WCTW1HAj08c
Part 4 (The Big Bad City)
